        <mxCell id="qBI2GgDgdt1LZkkiw9FO-218" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="CPU write load_flag = 1 to enter S_LOAD:&lt;div&gt;At S_LOAD: CPU write 16x 32-bit data values to memory&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;CPU write start_flag = 1 to enter S_EXEC&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;At S_EXEC: controller will output CTRL_MM_rd_en_i to get M_i [511:0] to SHA256 block and output M_valid_i to SHA256 to calculate at 1 clock clycle.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;After SHA256 calculation completing,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Store hash_o to memory&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Hash_valid_o will send to controller.v to notify SHA256 block done. Controller will trigger hash_valid_flag = 1. and move to S_READ state.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;CPU read hash_valid_flag, when hash_valid_flash = 1, CPU will read 8x 32-bit từ memory, sau đó CPU write done_flag to move S_IDLE state.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
